      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00226"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb133" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><date>14.&#160;6.&#160;05</date></dateline></opener><p>Herzlichsten Dank, <salute>lieber Arthur, </salute>für Deinen
